libsandbox
----------

Simple Linux sandbox using

* seccomp: Restrict system calls.
* Namespaces: Isolate processes, network, filesystem, etc.
* cgroups: Limit CPU, memory, and I/O.
* Capabilities: Drop unnecessary privileges.
* Filesystem Isolation: Use chroot or mount namespaces.

Dependencies
------------

libseccomp

Build
-----

make
sudo make install
